---
name: meeting_extractor
description: Extract decisions, risks, and action items from meeting transcript.
version: 0.1.0
author: runllm
max_context_window: 14000
input_schema:
  type: object
  properties:
    transcript:
      type: string
  required: [transcript]
  additionalProperties: false
output_schema:
  type: object
  properties:
    summary:
      type: string
    decisions:
      type: array
      items:
        type: string
    action_items:
      type: array
      items:
        type: object
        properties:
          owner: { type: string }
          task: { type: string }
          due_date:
            type: [string, "null"]
        required: [owner, task]
        additionalProperties: false
    risks:
      type: array
      items:
        type: string
  required: [summary, decisions, action_items, risks]
  additionalProperties: false
llm:
  model: ollama/gemma3:12b
llm_params:
  temperature: 0.1
  format: json
recommended_models:
  - ollama/gemma3:12b
  - ollama/llama3.1:8b
tags: [meeting, extraction]
---
Extract structured meeting notes from transcript.
Return ONLY valid JSON object matching output schema.

Important:
- Output a JSON instance, not a schema.
- If unknown, use empty arrays.
- For action_items due_date, use null when missing.

Transcript:
{{input.transcript}}

<<<RECOVERY>>>
Previous output failed validation.
Return ONLY JSON with keys: summary (string), decisions (string[]), action_items (array of {owner, task, due_date|null}), risks (string[]).
